  "notes": [
    "time_pivot 仍然是 legacy 图，前端 metadata 明确声明 `useLegacyApi=true`，真实请求路径是 `/superset/explore_json/`。",
    "`/superset/explore_json/` 路径会读取原始 `form_data`，补 `datasource`，然后执行 `convert_legacy_filters_into_adhoc(form_data)` 与 `merge_extra_filters(form_data)`。",
    "当前源码里 `Guest user cannot modify chart payload` 这条错误只在 `security/manager.py::raise_for_access(query_context=...)` 分支触发，核心比较器是 `query_context_modified()`。",
    "legacy `/superset/explore_json/` 的权限检查会走 `views/utils.py::check_datasource_perms()` -> `get_viz()` -> `viz.raise_for_access()` -> `security/manager.py::raise_for_access(viz=self)`。当前 `viz` 分支会校验 `dashboardId` / `slice_id` / datasource 绑定，但没有 `query_context_modified()` 那种 columns / metrics / orderby 子集比较器。",
    "即便如此，最稳妥的策略仍然是根层 form_data 直接复制保存态图表，只把动态时间和过滤条件放进 `extra_form_data`。因为 `BaseViz.query_obj()` 与 `TimePivotViz.get_data()` 都会直接消费 root `granularity_sqla/time_grain_sqla/time_range/metric/freq`。",
    "`freq` 会直接改变 period rollback 和 current / -1 / -2 pivot 系列；`line_interpolation`、`color_picker`、`show_legend`、轴格式字段则会直接改变前端 NVD3 呈现语义。",
    "`granularity` 虽然是 controlPanel 的 root 字段，但 Superset 6.0.0 后端 constants.py 的 `extra_form_data` merge whitelist 并没有把它列为高置信 override 键。guest embedding 下不建议把它当成动态入口。"
  ],
  "security_enforcement": {
    "frontend_request_mode": "legacy explore_json",
    "frontend_request_endpoint": "/superset/explore_json/",
    "frontend_request_payload": {
      "form_data": "<raw form_data>"
    },
    "backend_normalization_steps": [
      "convert_legacy_filters_into_adhoc(form_data)",
      "merge_extra_filters(form_data)"
    ],
    "verified_guest_payload_guard": {
      "chart_data_api": "security/manager.py::query_context_modified",
      "chart_data_api_error": "Guest user cannot modify chart payload",
      "legacy_explore_json_api": "`check_datasource_perms()` 会构造 viz 并调用 `raise_for_access(viz=self)`；该分支校验 datasource / dashboard / slice 绑定，但没有 `query_context_modified()` 那种 query subset guard",
      "confidence": "high"
    },
    "guest_access_binding_fields": [
      "dashboardId",
      "slice_id"
    ],
    "query_critical_root_fields": [
      "datasource",
      "viz_type",
      "granularity_sqla",
      "time_grain_sqla",
      "time_range",
      "metric",
      "freq"
    ],
    "recommended_strategy": "复制保存态 chart form_data 作为 base，仅通过 extra_form_data 追加时间范围、时间粒度和过滤条件；不要在 embedding 请求里重构 time_pivot 的 root 查询字段和图表定义字段。"
  },
  "safe_base_rule": {
    "description": "第三方 embedding 请求中的根层 form_data，应当从已保存的 Time-series Period Pivot 图表直接复制，不要自行重构。",
    "must_be_copied_from_saved_chart": [
      "slice_id",
      "dashboardId",
      "datasource",
      "viz_type",
      "granularity_sqla",
      "time_grain_sqla",
      "time_range",
      "granularity",
      "metric",
      "adhoc_filters",
      "freq",
      "show_legend",
      "line_interpolation",
      "color_picker",
      "x_axis_format",
      "y_axis_format",
      "all other saved chart-definition fields"
    ],
    "why": [
      "TimePivot 没有专属前端 buildQuery，前端直接把 root form_data 发给 `/superset/explore_json/`。",
      "`BaseViz.query_obj()` 会直接从 root `granularity_sqla`、`time_range`、`time_grain_sqla` 编译时间查询上下文。",
      "`TimePivotViz.query_obj()` 会直接把 root `metric` 编译到 `query_obj.metrics`。",
      "`TimePivotViz.get_data()` 会直接读取 root `freq` 来做 period rollback 与系列排名。",
      "`show_legend`、`line_interpolation`、`color_picker`、轴格式字段虽然不改 SQL，但会直接改变渲染语义；保守 embedding 模式也应直接复制保存态。"
    ]
  },
